Package io.helidon.microprofile.reactive.hybrid

Interface HybridSubscription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Flow.Subscription, org.reactivestreams.Subscription
    public interface HybridSubscription
extends Flow.Subscription, org.reactivestreams.Subscription
    Wrapper for Reactive Streams Subscription or Helidon reactive streams Flow.Subscription, to be used interchangeably.
